      • getBoundingBox

        public BoundingBox getBoundingBox()
        Returns the BoundingBox of the Shape. If the BoundingBox has not been calculated before, it will happen before returning it, but it will not be recalculated, if it already exists. If you've added any new points that should be considered in the BoundingBox, remove or recalculate the BoundingBox before calling this method.
        Returns:
        the BoundingBox of the Shape
